{"title":"Pedal a Pair of SMITH Gravel Shoes or QUOC Sunglasses & Helmet in LTD Strata Collab","link":"https://bikerumor.com/pedal-a-pair-of-smith-gravel-shoes-or-quoc-sunglasses-helmet-in-ltd-strata-collab/","date":1777482050000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_Smith-branded-shoes-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: limited edition gravel shoes helmet and shades collab, Quoc Gran Tourer XC gravel shoes\" /></p>\n<p>OK, so the new SMITH x QUOC Strata Collection is really just a limited edition collaboration between the 61-year-old eyewear &amp; helmet maker and the 17-year-old shoe company. But to gravel fans of either brand – of which there are plenty – it’s also a nice, rare chance to get a pair of Smith-branded gravel shoes or a set of Quoc-labelled sunglasses and a new helmet.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, Quoc also has a sneaky habit of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/quoc-x-maap-collab-reshapes-ltd-gran-tourer-xc-gravel-shoes-teases-spring-colors/\" target=\"_blank\">slipping in new tech</a> when they introduce a new collab project… </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>SMITH x QUOC limited edition Strata Collection collaboration</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: limited edition gravel shoes helmet and shades collab, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding.jpg 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-2048x1229.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Strata-Collection_limited-edition-gravel-shoes-helmet-and-shades-collab_dusty-riding-1500x900.jpg 1500w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Quoc)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The two brands describe a shared love of riding gravel, and Strata is their way to showcase some “<em>sandstone sediment-evoking hues</em>” in their common interests. The Smith x Quoc Strata collection includes just four elements, pulling two from each company’s existing line-up in a special color with limited edition graphics.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-1536x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Smith QUOC\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter4-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-1536x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Smith QUOC\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter5-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-1536x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Smith QUOC\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-helmets-sea-otter6-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Smith had a secret speakeasy at Sea Otter where the new Stratta Collab was on display. We heard there was some <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NVoy3mMxvCo\" target=\"_blank\">mezcal &amp; tequila too</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Quoc Strata Gran Tourer XC Lace</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Quoc Gran Tourer XC gravel shoes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_on-the-rocks-1600x900.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Flagship on the shoe side is the Smith x Quoc Gran Tourer XC Lace, now also with Smith logos on the left shoe. The top of their performance line-up, the shoes combine Quoc’s classic durable synthetic upper, stiffest carbon-composite sole construction with molded-on TPU tread lugs, wrap-around rubber protection, and hard-to-argue-with double-lock laces. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>They also feature a new ribbed TPU-laminated tongue construction (in light blue) with larger perforations that Quoc says improves both foot comfort and overall breathability of the shoes. In fact, it looks like the same new tongue debuted last year on the wire-laced version of these shoes in the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/quoc-x-maap-collab-reshapes-ltd-gran-tourer-xc-gravel-shoes-teases-spring-colors/\">MAAP collab</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Quoc Gran Tourer XC gravel shoes, pair\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair.jpg 2500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-2048x1229.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_pair-1500x900.jpg 1500w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The limited edition $310 / 265€ Quoc Tourer XC Lace shoes get a Sandstone-colored upper with a “fossilized” print, highlighted by bleu opal tongue and logos, plus pink &amp; purple Jade accents. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Quoc Gran Tourer XC gravel shoes with special laces\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces-297x260.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces-1536x1344.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces-120x105.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces-768x672.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Gran-Tourer-XC-Lace_limited-edition-gravel-shoes_crazy-laces-1029x900.jpg 1029w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They also come with both the standard low-key Sandstone laces and more flashy, serrated-edge purple Jade laces for extra style points. </p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Smith Strata Defy sunglasses</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Smith Defy sunglasses\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses-1600x900.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s start with the shades, since that’s what Smith has been making since 1965. These $207 / 185€ Strata edition Defy sunnies are a new color option of Smith’s most popular shades. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Smith Defy sunglasses, side view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Defy-limited-edition-Strata-sunglasses_side-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They get a matching Sandstone fossil print, but sadly no Quoc-branding on the rimless TR90 nylon-framed glasses themselves. Although they do come with a co-branded carry bag, plus an interchangeable clear lens for those dark rides when the huge, high-contrast ChromaPop shaded lens is just too dark.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Smith Strata Trace MIPS vented road helmet</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Smith Trace MIPS helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head.jpg 2100w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_on-head-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The fully-vented $300 / 265€ Smith x Quoc Strata Trace MIPS road helmet in matching fossil Sandstone print does get proper Quoc co-branding, though. The 18-vent Trace MIPS helmet hasn’t really changed much <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/smith-gets-more-aero-w-new-ignite-trace-road-helmets-hides-behind-giant-shades/\" target=\"_blank\">in many years</a>, but that’s because it has a been a popular mainstay in the Smith line-up, combining the dual safety systems of MIPS rotational impact protection and open Koroyd impact-absorbing honeycomb.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Smith Trace MIPS helmet, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile.jpg 2100w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_side-profile-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Smith x Quoc Strata collaboration edition combines the matching two-tone shell with purple Jade webbing and some little blue Opal details. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd. ed. Smith Trace MIPS helmet with sunglasses storage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Smith-x-Quoc-Trace-MIPS-limited-edition-Strata-vented-road-helmet_Defy-glasses-stash-1600x900.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides MIPS &amp; Koroyd, it comes in three s, M &amp; L sizes (51-62cm fit), and also gets VaporFit 270° dial fit adjustment, Ionic+ antimicrobial padding, and side vent openings to stow your Defy shades.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Quoc Strata Performance Gravel Socks</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: ltd ed lightweight performance gravel socks\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks.jpg 2100w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-collaboration_Performance-Gravel-Socks-1350x900.jpg 1350w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These Strata socks are also an all-new product for Quoc, a lighter synthetic blend for hot days riding mixed surfaces. The  $35 / 30€ Smith x Quoc Strata Performance Gravel Socks are a mash-up of Quoc’s lighter road and more structured, high-wear gravel offerings. They are made of a more breathable 67% CoolMax blend, backed by a mix of polyester, nylon &amp; elastic for comfort, stretchy fit, and durability. The co-branded limited edition socks come in two color-block versions – purple Jade or Sandstone, each with alternating accents.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2150\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration.jpg\" alt=\"Smith x Quoc Strata Collection: limited edition gravel shoes helmet and shades collab, sitting on a rock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-279x300.jpg 279w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-1536x1651.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-112x120.jpg 112w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-768x826.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-1429x1536.jpg 1429w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-1905x2048.jpg 1905w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SMITH-x-QUOC-limited-edition-Strata-Collection-gravel-collaboration-837x900.jpg 837w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All four limited edition products are available both from <a href=\"https://www.smithoptics.com/en-us/collections/smith-x-quoc\" target=\"_blank\">Smith</a> and <a href=\"https://quoc.cc/en-eu/collections/smith-x-quoc\" target=\"_blank\">Quoc</a> now, exclusively online and in limited numbers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://quoc.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Quoc.cc</a></em> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.smithoptics.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>SmithOptics.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pedal-a-pair-of-smith-gravel-shoes-or-quoc-sunglasses-helmet-in-ltd-strata-collab/\">Pedal a Pair of SMITH Gravel Shoes or QUOC Sunglasses &amp; Helmet in LTD Strata Collab</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"86c054f70b0e0415fcf5d6b52a40ed9eede7f0a78637928e7f3ecffc11c1e511","category":"Cycling"}